{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":1162482,"duration_api_ms":1153510,"num_turns":16,"result":"No errors in EntityStateMachine. The pre-existing errors are in unrelated files (`RedisStreamBacklogMetrics`, `IngestionRequestValidator`).\n\n## Summary\n\nTwo bugs in `EntityStateMachine.processStage()`:\n\n**Bug 1 — Uncaught exceptions leave entities permanently stuck** (the main issue you're seeing):\n- When `txRunner::runPolicy` throws a RuntimeException (NPE, connection error, etc.), it propagates out of `processStage()`, skipping the DB update entirely\n- Entity stays at `LABELED` with `processingCode=0` forever\n- Recovery job finds it, retries, same exception → infinite loop\n- **Fix**: Wrap `serviceFunction.apply(dto)` in try-catch, converting exceptions to `SYSTEM_ERROR (-1)`, which triggers the retry mechanism. After 3 retries, the error code is persisted and the entity is marked as failed.\n\n**Bug 2 — Stage advances unconditionally, even on failure**:\n- `dto.setProcessingStage(nextStage)` ran regardless of success/failure\n- A failed policy evaluation would show `stage=EVALUATED, code=3200` — misleading since evaluation never succeeded\n- **Fix**: Only call `setProcessingStage(nextStage)` when `serviceSuccess=true`. Failed entities now stay at the stage where they failed (e.g., `LABELED` with `code=3200`), making it clear where the problem is.","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"65a76568-ed84-4d6f-aa75-bda3984bc443","total_cost_usd":0.6853082500000002,"usage":{"input_tokens":2974,"cache_creation_input_tokens":43405,"cache_read_input_tokens":378485,"output_tokens":6988,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":43405,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-opus-4-6[1m]":{"inputTokens":2975,"outputTokens":7290,"cacheReadInputTokens":433804,"cacheCreationInputTokens":43405,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.6853082500000002,"contextWindow":1000000,"maxOutputTokens":64000}},"permission_denials":[],"terminal_reason":"completed","fast_mode_state":"off","uuid":"dc4765e2-ffa4-40c9-826c-15c30a9fd3c9"}
